item.title: WinFellow has a new home
item.description: WinFellow development has found a new home on GitHub; please update your bookmarks accordingly. Downloads for older releases are still available at SourceForge for reference; for future news and updates, please visit us here. The GitHub source code repository is available here. Future releases of WinFellow will be published in GitHub’s releases section.
